nity yesterday as Russia is saying, or can you rule that out?<o:p></o:p></p=
>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; I'd encourage you to check with t=
he Department of Defense on that.&nbsp; They can give you some updated info=
rmation.&nbsp; I certainly have not heard anything to lend any credibility
 to that kind of a statement, but check with DOD.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Okay.&nbsp; And former Speaker B=
