 to it?<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; Well, obviously Speaker Boehner w=
as speaking based on his own experience.&nbsp; (Laughter.)&nbsp; And I&#821=
7;m not sure that he was trying to do -- I don&#8217;t know that he was loo=
king to
 be helpful or harmful; I think he was just looking to be honest about his =
own view.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tex=
t-indent:.5in">
Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Just being honest.&nbsp; But when words like that are u=
sed and phrases and descriptions are thrown out there, as they have been in=
 this election, do you consider that crossing a line?<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tex=
t-indent:.5in">
&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tex=
t-indent:.5in">
MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; Look, I think if you&#8217;re looking for somebody to co=
