d of technology could be effectively used to make guns safer.&nbsp; And so =
this is something that a variety of federal agencies have reviewed, and the=
y'll have some findings to share.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
