<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; I haven't seen the details of thi=
s particular piece of legislation.&nbsp; I can just tell you as a general m=
atter, Chris, as you've heard me say on a number of occasions in the
 last few weeks, the administration believes strongly in fairness, in equal=
ity, and justice.&nbsp; And we believe in bills that promote fairness, equa=
lity, and justice, and we are strongly opposed to any legislative effort to=
