e of any impact it had.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt">&n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; And just to be clear, you're not=
