on that would bring an end to the violence inside of Syria.&nbsp; It&#8217;=
s why we have regularly been in touch with the Russians
 to encourage them to use their influence with the Assad regime to live up =
to the cessation of hostilities and engage in the political talks.<o:p></o:=
p></p>
